Testcase Design
1. Log in as standard_user.
2. Verify that the correct error messages appears if username is left blank
3. Verify that the correct error messages appears if password is left blank
4. Add items to cart and verify that the cart count reflect correctly
5. Verify if items are sorted correctly base on price (high to low).
6. Verify if items are sorted correctly base on Letter (A to Z).
7. Proceed to Checkout items
8. Verify error displayed if some or all required fields are in checkout screen left unpopulated
9. Fill all the required fields
10. Verify  order details 
11. Verify Successful order message 
12. Add items to Cart
13. Remove items to cart
14. Verify if cart are empty


Which 3 Testcase are to automate first?
Testcase 1-3 for the main reason that It is the most if not test case that are repetitive and most scenarios go through it as its pre-requisites
